title: Watch NASA's Artemis 2 moon rocket on the launch pad with this 24-hour livestream
description: The Artemis 2 moon mission's SLS rocket is on the pad at Kennedy Space Center for testing ahead of a possible Feb. 6 launch, and you can watch it 24/7 via this livestream.
